tags (e.g. ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0-rc3","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":").","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Import the librairies you need","anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" products.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Tip","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"tip"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","level":3},{"type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and useless constants.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Import the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" product which suits your needs:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Umbrella","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUI","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above and all themes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]]},{"type":"heading","text":"Chose your theme","anchor":"Chose-your-theme","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" framework provides today four themes:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Theme","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Sosh","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For Sosh products","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Wireframe","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]]},{"type":"heading","text":"Apply a theme","anchor":"Apply-a-theme","level":3},{"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to use for your application root view the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" also."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":1},{"content":[{"code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"size":1}]},{"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":1},{"content":[{"code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"size":1}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Tip","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"tip"},{"type":"heading","text":"Trick for Xcode Preview","anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you use Xcode ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"inside the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OU